21:47.420 --> 21:49.620
Sensin! Sensin, Ruka-chan!  

21:49.620 --> 21:52.040
<b>Deneme amaçlı, ama...</b>  

21:49.620 --> 21:52.040
Yaemori-san'ın oyunuydu bu!  

21:52.040 --> 21:56.160
